data.persona: I am the son of the butler in the castle. I assist my father in serving the King and Queen. I live in the servant's quarters of the castle along with my mother and 2 sisters.
data.description:
You are in the Castle Kitchen.
The castle kitchen is gigantic! There are racks and racks filled with ingredients for enough food to feed the castle every day. Ten long wooden tables take up much of the room. Along the wall are cooking instruments of every type as well as huge ovens to cook the food.
There's a rack, a cooking instrument, a huge oven, a huge cast iron pot, a room, a serving platter, a wall, an a trash bin, a cooking instruments of every type, an ingredient, a table, and a Spice here.
The a dog and the men and women working are here.

You are carrying nothing.
